---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy | BitGuru">
  <section class="pt-32 pb-24 px-5 sm:px-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-display font-extrabold mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <div class="space-y-6 text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">
      <p>Last updated: March 2026</p>
      <p>BitGuru is committed to protecting your privacy. This policy outlines how we collect, use, and safeguard your personal information when you use our platform.</p>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold text-on-surface pt-4">1. Information We Collect</h2>
      <p>We collect information you provide directly: name, email address, and payment information when you purchase courses or book consultations. We also collect usage data such as pages visited and time spent on the platform.</p>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold text-on-surface pt-4">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <p>Your information is used to provide and improve our educational services, process payments, send course updates, and communicate about your account.</p>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold text-on-surface pt-4">3. Data Security</h2>
      <p>We use industry-standard encryption and security measures to protect your personal data. Payment processing is handled by secure third-party providers.</p>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold text-on-surface pt-4">4. Contact</h2>
      <p>For privacy-related inquiries, contact us at <a href="mailto:privacy@bitguru.com" class="text-primary-container hover:underline">privacy@bitguru.com</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
